{"id":38250,"date":"2024-02-29T11:16:00","date_gmt":"2022-09-30T05:46:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=38250"},"modified":"2023-09-30T12:28:19","modified_gmt":"2023-09-30T06:58:19","slug":"sleeper-sofa-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sleeper-sofa-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Sleeper Sofa Ideas To Up The Comfort Quotient Of Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Change the mood and ambience of your dream home with these sleeper sofa designs that have taken the interior industry by surprise.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Everyone loves a good home interior setting, one that incorporates all the elements of a complete home. However, due to space constraints, we are always compromising on finding the perfect fit for our living space. While you may love to have a decent three-seater sofa with accent chairs, they may not be a good choice if you are hosting guests time and again and need an extra sleeping space. This is where sleeper sofas come in handy. With that being said, we have designed five stunning living spaces that can easily incorporate your next seating upgrade, aka, sleeper sofas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Grey Full-Size Sleeper Sofa For A Large Living And Entertainment Area<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You have a lovely modular TV unit that extends into a study and a coffee table seated between accent chairs, but feel your living room needs just a tiny upgrade? Complete the overall aesthetics of your space with a lovely full-size sleeper sofa bed in grey. Pair it with a white faux fur rug underneath. This setup is perfect for large homes that need an extra bed for the night.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111209\/full-size-sleeper-sofa-in-grey.jpg\" alt=\"A full-sized grey sleeper sofa paired with a white faux fur rug in living room\" class=\"wp-image-38251\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111209\/full-size-sleeper-sofa-in-grey.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111209\/full-size-sleeper-sofa-in-grey-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111209\/full-size-sleeper-sofa-in-grey-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111209\/full-size-sleeper-sofa-in-grey-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Add an entertainer seat to your living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Venture Into Long Movies Nights With This Blue Boxed Sleeper Sofa Set<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you love a good movie marathon and need to retire into a comfortable seating space, then this blue boxed full-size sleeper sofa bed does the job. Accentuated with a modular lift-top coffee table in white that stores all your movie time snacks and electric gadgets, this living room setting doubles up as your weekend entertainment spot.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111240\/sleeper-sofa-set-blue-boxed.jpg\" alt=\"Blue boxed sleeper sofa set accentuated with a modular lift-top coffee table\" class=\"wp-image-38256\" style=\"width:840px;height:504px\" width=\"840\" height=\"504\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111240\/sleeper-sofa-set-blue-boxed.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111240\/sleeper-sofa-set-blue-boxed-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111240\/sleeper-sofa-set-blue-boxed-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111240\/sleeper-sofa-set-blue-boxed-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Retire into comfortable seating for movie nights<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180939\/end-to-end-home-interior-design-solutions-for-stunning-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Channel Tufted Single Sleeper Sofa For Your Guest Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/guest-room-design-ideas\/\">guest room<\/a> is the only space in your home that needs a little attention and can often be overlooked. However, adding a tufted single sleeper sofa with throw pillows can help bring a sense of comfort and belonging to this space. Add a few indoor plants, a guest storage cabinet with drawers and you are good to go.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111228\/single-sleeper-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Guest room where adding a single sleeper sofa with throw pillows brings a sense of comfort\" class=\"wp-image-38254\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111228\/single-sleeper-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111228\/single-sleeper-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111228\/single-sleeper-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111228\/single-sleeper-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Single sleeper sofa in the guest room for comfort<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">You Can Replace Your Bed With This Tufted Queen Sleeper Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you like to get a little adventurous and need to upgrade your bedroom space, you can choose to replace your boxed bed with this tufted queen sleeper sofa. When not in need, you can always fold it back down to a three-seater sofa saving you enough space in the day to run errands around. You can complement this queen sleeper sofa bed with a ceiling-to-floor wardrobe and marble top side tables with lamps on either side of the bed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111223\/queen-sleeper-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom with a tufted queen sofa doubles up as a three-seater sofa saving enough space\" class=\"wp-image-38253\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111223\/queen-sleeper-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111223\/queen-sleeper-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111223\/queen-sleeper-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111223\/queen-sleeper-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Have a good night\u2019s sleep with this tufted sofa bed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go Chic With A Minimalist Sleeper Sofa Instead Of A Modern Sofa Set<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Just like the bedroom, you can also switch your living room\u2019s conventional sofa sets with this minimalist sleeper sofa set in grey. Adding to the perfection of a reading haven, this sleeper sofa can best suit the bibliophile in you for times you need to retire with your favourite read.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111215\/minimalist-sleeper-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Open living room in minimalist design that has reading nook with a sleeper sofa\" class=\"wp-image-38252\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111215\/minimalist-sleeper-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111215\/minimalist-sleeper-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111215\/minimalist-sleeper-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/29111215\/minimalist-sleeper-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A modern minimalist sleeper sofa for a reading nook<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know how you can accentuate your living space with a unique furnishing option, why not try out these sleeper sofa sets at your home as well? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">Book a free consultation<\/a> with expert designers at DesignCafe and get yourself a virtual tour of your dream home today!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the meantime, check out some of our popular blogs on home interior design tips and ideas below:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/plant-decoration-in-living-room\/\">The ultimate guide to decorating your home with plants<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/rustic-home-decor-ideas\/\">Rustic home decor ideas for the decor enthusiast in you<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/dorm-room-ideas\/\">Accentuate your dorm room with these unique decor ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wooden-false-ceiling\/\">Wooden false ceiling ideas that add charm to any home setting<\/a><\/li>\